"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-when-will-tatjana-schoenmaker-smith-swim-200m-breaststroke-olympic-final\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9990150097712631, \"rank\": 0.0009858657141220888, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbWhen will Tatjana swim in 200m breaststroke Olympic final?\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9990150097712631, \"rank\": 0.0009858657141220888, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tatjana Smith will take part in the 200m breaststroke Olympic final on Thursday night.\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 350, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here is when to catch her in action.\", \"from\": 351, \"to\": 387, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tatjana Smithwill go in search of a historic medalwhen she competes in another Olympic final on Thursday night, this time in her favourite 200m breaststroke event.\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 552, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith was widely expected to win her semi-final, but on Wednesday she finished just behind surprise winner Kate Douglass.\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 675, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 661, \"end\": 674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Douglass\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kate Douglass\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Douglass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Douglass\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nevertheless, there were various strategies and recovery management plans in place for Tatjana as she comfortably booked her place in the Olympic final.\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 828, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Certainly if Smith can grab a gold medal in Thursday night's women's 200m breaststroke final at the 2024 Paris Olympics, she would almost certainly become South Africa's greatest-ever Olympian.\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 1023, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 985, \"end\": 997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999969818418, \"rank\": 3.017797533173646e-09, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 1014, \"end\": 1022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999846627362, \"rank\": 1.5337463682542146e-08, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Any top three placing would take her overall medals tally to four - while if she wins on Thursday night, she would have the tally of three golds and a silver.\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1183, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In this scenario, although she would join Chad le Clos on four medals, no other Olympian would boast her 'weight' of medals in terms of golds and silvers.\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1226, \"end\": 1238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad_le_Clos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chad le Clos\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad_le_Clos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad_le_Clos\"}, {\"begin\": 1264, \"end\": 1272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999846627362, \"rank\": 1.5337463682542146e-08, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It should certainly not be forgotten that Smith will be joined in the final by extremely talentedKaylene Corbett, whoimpressively finished secondin the first semi-final.\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1445, \"end\": 1452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_J._Corbett\", \"score\": 0.7447516535107253, \"rank\": 0.27131573325109565, \"text\": \"Corbett\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_J._Corbett\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_J._Corbett\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The highly anticipatedfinal is expected to take place just after 21:00 on Thursday, 1 August, with SuperSport expecting the swimmers to hit the water at about 21:11 - give or take a few minutes.\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1705, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, there will also be plenty of attention on Le Clos when he takes part in the 100m butterfly event this year, and hewill be in action on Friday, 2 August, in heat two - which will get under way around11am (SA time).\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1931, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As a boy I never dreamed of going to the Olympic Games,\\\" he told theTeam SA websiteas he touched on his emotions at what will be his final Olympics.\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 2082, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2007, \"end\": 2009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0114107370612778e-17, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To be here representing the country again, wearing the green and gold, honestly, there is no higher honour than that for me.\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2209, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In London I was such a green boy.\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2213, \"end\": 2219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999999668034, \"rank\": 3.102383208742986e-11, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then came Rio and that was followed by the Covid Olympics.\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2254, \"end\": 2257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999506649159, \"rank\": 4.9335026887126e-08, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, it's Paris.\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2313, \"end\": 2318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999995366124, \"rank\": 4.6352502801297247e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's bittersweet though.\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I suffered a shoulder tear four weeks ago when a kid jumped on me when I was swimming and my shoulder popped out.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2458, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It will have recovered but the inflammation and damage done has affected me.\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2535, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Three weeks ago I was crying every day.\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2575, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will be devastated if I can not compete \\u2026 it will be one of the worst moments in my career,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2681, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have put so much into it.\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2710, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am now 32, a ballie, a pensioner in swimming terms.\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2764, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My body feels like it's 40.\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have bled for this sport, bled for my country.\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a patriot.\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2857, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been written off so many times, but I can assure you, if my shoulder holds up, I will make that final and then watch out.\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2986, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a dog.\", \"from\": 2987, \"to\": 2998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not crumble under the lights or pressure.\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3045, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will be in the mix.\", \"from\": 3046, \"to\": 3067, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Quote me on that.\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3085, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am still good, I am still good enough to win races, titles and medals.\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether it happens here we will see.\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3197, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If not it will happen going forward.\", \"from\": 3198, \"to\": 3234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am still leaving it all out here.\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I moved to Germany to prepare for these Olympics.\", \"from\": 3271, \"to\": 3320, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3282, \"end\": 3289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.9990268629947918, \"rank\": 0.0009351231469034097, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With respect, I do not like the place.\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3359, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's\\u00a0not for me, do you know what I mean?\", \"from\": 3360, \"to\": 3401, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a South African, I am a patriot.\", \"from\": 3402, \"to\": 3439, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I thrive when surrounded by South Africans.\\\"\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3484, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 3486, \"to\": 3565, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3486, \"end\": 3489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"score\": 0.9999795797273185, \"rank\": 2.0420659100358764e-05, \"text\": \"WIN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\"}, {\"begin\": 3490, \"end\": 3492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"score\": 0.9985373924011285, \"rank\": 0.0011922714084801967, \"text\": \"R2\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Freelance writing positions available  Follow The South African on Facebook for the latest local and international news  Follow The South African's WhatsApp channel for the latest sport, lifestyle and local news  Follow The South African on X for the latest, breaking news  A brand new shopping mall is coming to Pretoria East, bringing major retailers and new convenience to the area.\", \"from\": 3566, \"to\": 3951, \"entities\"